{"tid":31580,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門雞飯","createTime":"2016-12-09T17:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T15:19:35.000Z","uid":62277,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a0a922d9878e7aadc935c8164e980afdc77ef57","tid":31580,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T17:59:52.000Z","msg":"名符其實既小店一間,入面十個位都無<br />\n我d港女fd話見到佢門口就覺得係垃圾<br />\n過我就最中意去呢d地方食野<br />\n個人口味會更中意佢既牛腩<br />\n不過份量比雞會少,唔合連登仔口味<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雞浸醃得清香,嫩滑、唔乾<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/c0mgfvtx\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fc0mgfvtx&h=b5e5e6d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下面仲有一層,一份有十舊左右<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qfkplioc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqfkplioc&h=34c9b569&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n包埋飯、菜、糖水各一,菜用雞湯浸,爽滑<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/aqwl2jt7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Faqwl2jt7&h=988ca010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南瓜西米露<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xcgq0nd8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxcgq0nd8&h=119fb9eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"593be1d8efbda29fe0f6a14001ff6bb427220d0f","tid":31580,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T18:05:53.000Z","msg":"幾點呀屌你"},{"pid":"b35123795be1635b515f14b23fbab36441c2d4af","tid":31580,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T18:05:59.000Z","msg":"係邊"},{"pid":"266f39932a2c74f0b7e4a65f915f035e4936f8b9","tid":31580,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T18:07:47.000Z","msg":"邊度啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj